## Canon PIXMA Paper Feed Issue

### Customer Issue

* Canon PIXMA G3416
* Paper pulled to one side
* Frequent paper jams

### Findings

* Printer feeds paper unevenly
* Possible roller or feed mechanism issue
* Unit may still be under warranty

### Resolution

* Recommended official warranty inspection
* Advised customer to contact authorized Canon service provider
* Avoided disassembly to protect warranty status

---

## When to Escalate

Escalate to authorized service center when:

* Internal feed mechanism failure
* Hardware faults
* Print head failure
* Warranty repairs required

---

## Preventive Maintenance

* Keep printer clean
* Use correct paper type
* Avoid overloading paper tray
* Keep drivers updated
* Perform periodic cleaning

